# Multi-shot capture example: several screenshots and a state dump from ONE
# emulator run. Frame numbers are emulator frames; with the bundled BIOS the
# cart gets control at roughly frame 60.
#
#   .\bin\gbarun.exe --rom test\dbg_smoke.gba --headless ^
#       --replay test\scripts\multi-shot.replay --frames 300
#
# Output paths are relative to the emulator's working directory (repo root).
80   screenshot bin/shot_f80.png
150  screenshot bin/shot_f150.png
200  dump-state bin/state_f200.txt
250  screenshot bin/shot_f250.png
